{"tid":2351564,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"葵興好住啲定青衣好住啲？","createTime":"2021-01-03T10:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T06:08:07.000Z","uid":123613,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"3dec444601025c26ca20cf8a36517fe2ec008b6c","tid":2351564,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:27:02.000Z","msg":"只係mtr站嗰頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得交通嚟講葵興好好多 東涌線星期六日同夜晚荔景等東涌線返青衣 紅色線可能去到荃灣東涌線車都未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有青衣嗰邊啲通宵車又係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋葵興嗰邊返工可以10分鐘步程內返到公司 青衣站嗰邊都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n論交通應該葵芳好啲 盈翠灝景都唔知點解可以貴過新葵興花園好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f8d837eeceaa10f5086000c5b982b1116a1d1c","tid":2351564,"uid":202511,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:27:49.000Z","msg":"青衣夜晚乜都冇"},{"pid":"7c7805031fa75ae09257fc706aa8f7454ddab1ae","tid":2351564,"uid":4826,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"葵興夜晚食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60e50523c7bf600a98816e2a401f417c344c667","tid":2351564,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:29:04.000Z","msg":"青衣"},{"pid":"d1e6a7e336a59f1531fd3056ab83e40beafb6ba7","tid":2351564,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a777603f537fd074a7c4be92a44d7f81d6faa23","tid":2351564,"uid":33468,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"新葵芳花園點同盈翠灝景比呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 盈翠灝景係靚好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\